    - AlertQuery - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Possible Misconfiguration of Auth0 Tenant Name: Displays a table of Successful Logins and Signups from Flagged IPs.  
    - AlertQuery - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Successful Login with Suspicious JA4 Fingerprint: Displays a table of Successful Login with Suspicious JA4 Fingerprint.  
    - AlertQuery - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Successful Logins and Signups from Flagged IPs: Displays a table of Successful Logins and Signups from Flagged IPs.  
    - AlertQuery - Auth0 - User - MFA - Possible Account Takeover: Displays a table of Possible Account Takeovers due to multiple users registered to the same deviceId and IP.  
- Naming Schema: *AlertQuery - Auth0 - System - Category/Logtype - Subcategory/Log Subtype - Severity/Priority - SearchName [Visualization - if any]*  

***  

## 9. [Templates](#9-templates)  

- Purpose: Templates are special objects which define a Gravwell query containing variables.  
- [Documentation](<https://docs.gravwell.io/gui/templates/templates.html>)  
- Total: ***8***  
    - Template - Auth0 - System - Log Types - Count by Category & Subcategory [chart]: Displays a chart of events by count performed by the specified User (user\_id or user\_name) and/or IP Address.  
    - Template - Auth0 - System - Log Types - Count by Category & Subcategory [numbercard]: Displays a numbercard of events by count performed by the specified User (user\_id or user\_name) and/or IP Address.  
    - Template - Auth0 - System - Log Types - Count by Category & Subcategory [table]: Displays a table of events by count performed by the specified User (user\_id or user\_name) and/or IP Address.  
    - Template - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Blocked Account [table]: Displays a table of events performed by a Blocked Account.  
    - Template - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Count by Category [numbercard]: Displays a numbercard of user authentication events by Authentication Category for the specified User (user\_id or user\_name) and/or IP Address.  
    - Template - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Failed Login [table]: Displays a table of failed login attempts with invalid usernames or non-existent users.  
    - Template - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Leaked Password Login Attempts [table]: Displays a table of events performed indicating a high number of login attempts using a leaked password.  
    - Template - Auth0 - User - Authentication - Successful Login [table]: Displays a table of successful logins.  

***  

## 10. [Dashboards](#10-dashboards)  

- Purpose: Dashboards are Gravwell’s way of showing the results from multiple searches at the same time.  
- [Documentation](<https://docs.gravwell.io/gui/dashboards/dashboards.html>)  
- Total: ***2***  
    - Auth0 General Overview: This Dashboard is a general overview of your Auth0 data.  
    - Auth0 Investigation: This dashboard is intended to be used for Auth0 investigations.  

#### 10.1. [Actionables](#10-1-actionables)  

- Purpose: Actionables provide a way to create custom menus that key on any text rendered in a query; users can take different actions on that text by selecting options in the menus.  
- [Documentation](<https://docs.gravwell.io/gui/actionables/actionables.html>)  
- Total: ***3***  
    - Auth0 IP: Auth0 actions on IP Addresses to Launch Auth0 Investigation Dashboard.  
    - Auth0 UserID: Auth0 actions on User Ids (userId) to Launch Auth0 Investigation Dashboard.  
    - Auth0 UserName: Auth0 actions on User Name (userName) to Launch Auth0 Investigation Dashboard.  

***  

